t="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sabrina-Carpenter.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sabrina-Carpenter.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sabrina-Carpenter.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sabrina-Carpenter.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sabrina-Carpenter.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sabrina-Carpenter.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter)</a>透露了参加她即将推出的 Netflix 假日特别节目“胡言乱语的圣诞节”的嘉宾名单。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sabrina-carpenter-short-n-sweet-review-3787293">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) – “Short n&#39; Sweet”评论：一位新的流行公主的崛起</a></strong></li></ul><p>卡彭特将在该节目中表演她 2023 年圣诞 EP“Fruitcake”中的歌曲，其中包括她 2022 年热门单曲“Nonsense”的节日版本，该节目将于美国东部时间 12 月 6 日星期五晚上 6 点（格林威治标准时间晚上 10 点）在 Netflix 上播出。</p><p>今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-a-nonsense-christmas-special-on-netflix-3795301">她开玩笑说她将有音乐剧和“喜剧嘉宾”加入</a>，今天（11 月 19 日）她透露了完整阵容。</p><p>在 Instagram 上分享的预告片中，卡彭特透露，她将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tyla">泰拉 (Tyla)</a>进行音乐二重唱，嘉宾包括尼科·希拉瓜 (Nico Hiragua)、昆塔·布伦森 (Quinta Brunson)、卡拉·迪瓦伊<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cara-delevingne">(Cara Delevingne</a> )、凯尔·穆尼 (Kyle Mooney)、梅根·斯塔尔特 (Megan Stalter)、西恩·奥斯汀 (Sean Astin)、欧文·蒂勒 (Owen Thiele) 和吉莉安·贝尔 (Jillian Bell)。</p><p>这段视频显示，布伦森出现在一部模仿<em>《圣诞颂歌》</em>的小品中，这位 <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/abbott-elementary-season-4-release-date-filming-3773233">雅培小学的</a></em>创作者兼明星在其中扮演了“现在的幽灵”，而卡彭特则扮演了“过去的幽灵”。看看下面。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DCiyL3IxFkN/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,